Key Pricing Page Patterns:
- 4-tier horizontal layout (not 3 - allows more flexibility)
- Features grouped by category (Core Features, Platform Access)
- All CTAs route to /request-demo (unified funnel)
- FAQ addresses objections below pricing
- Social proof ("87% reduction in reporting time") near pricing

