- CTA button at bottom



================================================================================
                          INTERACTION PATTERNS
================================================================================

---
BUTTON BEHAVIORS
---
┌────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│    Button Type     │                      Behavior                           │
├────────────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Primary CTA        │ Solid fill, hover: slight darken/lift                   │
│                    │ Often includes arrow icon (→)                           │
│                    │ Example: "Get started now", "Buy Template"              │
├────────────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Secondary CTA      │ Outline or lighter fill                                 │
│                    │ Hover: fill change                                      │
│                    │ Example: "Explore more", "Contact us"                   │
├────────────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Text Link CTA      │ Arrow icon suffix                                       │
│                    │ Hover: underline or arrow animation                     │
│                    │ Example: "Continue reading →", "See integration →"      │
├────────────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Small Button       │ Reduced padding variant                                 │
│                    │ Used in cards and inline contexts                       │
└────────────────────┴─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

---
LINK STYLES
---
- Navigation links: No underline, hover color change
- Inline text links: Underlined or color differentiated
- Footer links: Lighter weight, subtle hover
- Arrow links: Icon animates on hover (→ shifts right)

---
