│ What are you interested in learning about?                      │
│ [▾ Select an option________________________]                    │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Any questions for the team?                                     │
│ [                                          ]                    │
│ [                                          ]                    │
│ [__________________________________________]                    │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ [ ] I consent to being contacted and agree to Privacy Policy    │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                    [Submit Request]                             │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

Validation Patterns:
- Client-side validation with error messaging
- Success: "Thank you! Your submission has been received!"
- Error: "Oops! Something went wrong while submitting the form."
- Required fields marked with asterisk

---
FAQ ACCORDION BEHAVIOR
---
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ [+] What integrations do you support?                           │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ [-] How long does setup take?                     (expanded)    │
│     Setup typically takes 2-3 days for basic                    │
│     configuration. Enterprise deployments may                   │
│     require additional time for custom integrations.            │
│                                                                 │
│     [Contact us →]                                              │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ [+] What about data security?                                   │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ [+] Can I cancel anytime?                                       │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

- Chevron icon rotates on expand/collapse
- Smooth height transition
- Only one section open at a time (single-select)
- Secondary CTA links within expanded content

---
SCROLL BEHAVIORS
---
- Sticky navigation: Fixed to top on scroll
- Scroll-triggered animations: Elements fade/slide in on viewport entry
- Parallax: Subtle on hero images (some pages)
- Smooth scroll: Anchor links animate to target

---
CAROUSEL INTERACTIONS
---
- Chevron navigation (left/right arrows)
- Auto-rotation (testimonial carousels)
- Pagination dots for position indication
- Touch/swipe support on mobile

---
MOBILE MENU BEHAVIOR
---
Trigger: Hamburger icon tap
Animation: Slide from right
Content: Full-height overlay with stacked links
Close: X icon or tap outside
Transition: Smooth slide with opacity



================================================================================
                       PERFORMANCE OBSERVATIONS
================================================================================

---
IMAGE OPTIMIZATION
---
┌──────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│       Technique          │                  Implementation                   │
├──────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Format                   │ WebP throughout (photo-art-*.webp naming)         │
├──────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Responsive Images        │ Multiple sizes served via srcset                  │
├──────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Lazy Loading             │ Native lazy loading on below-fold images          │
├──────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Hero Images              │ Prioritized loading (no lazy)                     │
├──────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ SVG Icons                │ Inline SVGs for interface elements                │
├──────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Logo Sprites             │ Individual optimized logos (not sprited)          │
└──────────────────────────┴───────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

---
ANIMATION PERFORMANCE
---
- CSS transforms used (translate3d) for GPU acceleration
- Opacity transitions for fade effects
- Staggered animations prevent layout thrashing
- Webflow Interactions 2.0 engine handles sequencing
- Mobile animations reduced (48px vs 72px offsets)

---
LOADING STRATEGIES
---
- Critical CSS inlined in head
- JavaScript deferred/async loading
- Font preloading for primary typeface
- Above-fold content prioritized
- YouTube embeds lazy-loaded (facade pattern likely)



